data.description: This charming brick ranch home in Lynwood has been beautifully updated! Inside, you'll discover 3 bedrooms on the main floor and an additional 2 bedrooms in the basement, complete with 3 modernized bathrooms. The spacious living room boasts a versatile fireplace that can burn wood or use gas. The basement is professionally waterproofed and fully finished, offering a movie theater and a bar for your enjoyment. Outside, you'll discover a gazebo with room for a projector and a large deck, perfect for hosting parties. Solar panels contribute to energy savings, and there's a convenient 2-car detached garage. Plus, there's a public park with a playground right behind the property for extra fun. Recent upgrades include new siding, roof, gutters, and soffits. The windows were replaced in 2016, and the furnace and A/C were upgraded in 2017.
